text: Dear Grandson,  As you may know I am Passing away Soon. I want to give you a Gift however before I pass Away. Im giving you Herritage Over my House. I belive I have Valuble Stuff You can sell (Or stuff you can Keep in my Memory). I also have a Console Never Released to the Public. Its called the Pix-6. it was a Test Console. It was meant to be Released to Fight in the "Console Wars" Or whatever you Kids call it these Days. But, The company went Bankrupt and it was never Released. It also has 1 Game that was Meant to Release With it.  Dont play the Game. I think It's Haunted. I remember Whenever I Played the Game as a Kid that same Night I Would Always Hear Noises Coming from the Console. One Night my Brother Woke Up. and He heard the Noises coming from the Console. I had to Convince him Not to Throw It Away. Needless to Say. Dont play it. Just Sell it. And Move on.  Forever Loving, Grandpa
